{"parentUuid":"06c55153-b045-4dfb-820e-de1834598702","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"fad29434-3192-4ff5-9837-386ddd92026c","agentId":"a0e2a387b4420ac2a","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_019omHKfuxECDuUoqZPPZxvK","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t//axhob_operation\n2\t{rbtgo_retriever_divest}\n3\t\n4\tNOTE: This operation divests a {rbtr_retriever} {giam_service_account} from the {rbtgi_depot_project}.\n5\tThe {rbtr_governor} reads the retriever's installed RBRA, extracts the SA email from the RBRA's `client_email` field, issues a REST DELETE against the IAM API, and removes the production RBRA file from disk to mirror cloud state and prevent stale-credential reuse.\n6\tNo arguments are required; the target SA is derived entirely from the kindled regime and the retriever's installed credential file.\n7\t\n8\t//axhos_step\n9\t. *Authenticate as {rbtr_governor}*:\n10\t.. Execute\n11\t{rbtoe_governor_authenticate}\n12\t.. {rbbc_store}\n13\t`«GOVERNOR_TOKEN»` for subsequent API calls\n14\t\n15\t//axhos_step\n16\t. *Read Retriever RBRA and Extract SA Email*:\n17\t.. {rbbc_require}\n18\tRBRA file present at\n19\t{rbrr_retriever_rbra_file}\n20\t.. {rbbc_fatal}\n21\tif file missing: \"Retriever RBRA file not found — retriever may not be invested\"\n22\t.. {rbbc_store}\n23\t`«RETRIEVER_EMAIL»` from RBRA's `client_email` field\n24\t.. {rbbc_fatal}\n25\tif `«RETRIEVER_EMAIL»` is empty or absent: \"client_email field missing from retriever RBRA\"\n26\t\n27\t//axhos_step\n28\t. *Delete Retriever Service Account*:\n29\t.. {rbbc_call}\n30\tlink:https://cloud.google.com/iam/docs/reference/rest/v1/projects.serviceAccounts/delete[iam.projects.serviceAccounts.delete] with:\n31\t... method: `DELETE`\n32\t... endpoint: `https://iam.googleapis.com/v1/projects/{rbtgi_depot_project}/serviceAccounts/«RETRIEVER_EMAIL»`\n33\t... header: `Authorization: Bearer «GOVERNOR_TOKEN»`\n34\t.. {rbbc_require}\n35\tHTTP 200 response OR HTTP 404 (already divested)\n36\t.. {rbbc_warn}\n37\tif HTTP 404: \"Retriever service account not found in cloud (already divested)\"\n38\t\n39\t//axhos_step\n40\t. *Remove Production RBRA File*:\n41\t.. Execute\n42\t{rbtoe_rbra_remove}\n43\tfor the retriever's RBRA file at\n44\t{rbrr_retriever_rbra_file},\n45\tmirroring cloud state and preventing stale-credential reuse\n46\t.. {rbbc_require}\n47\tfile removal successful or file already absent\n48\t\n49\t//axhos_step\n50\t. *Display Result*:"}]},"uuid":"0e78fe42-7414-4fd1-9f70-0cdccbd1415a","timestamp":"2026-04-27T22:03:34.122Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"06c55153-b045-4dfb-820e-de1834598702","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/bhyslop/projects/rbm_alpha_recipemuster","sessionId":"6ec50147-62d6-42fc-9c0a-3a89b7ebe356","version":"2.1.119","gitBranch":"main"}
